{"tid":2152788,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"#FreeAgnes成Twitter榜首  日本朝野名人 聲援周庭","createTime":"2020-08-12T07:41:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-12T07:42:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bab585037473750f51fa74c80f1014c9ec79d815","tid":2152788,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:41:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ITWJ3VLXUSACFHCLDS6QZWN2UU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FITWJ3VLXUSACFHCLDS6QZWN2UU%2F&d=xm989VH5JK0%2BokU91cWWfyJMs%2BH1ZGqELk%2BE%2F7wpkaY%3D&h=826d033b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200812%2FITWJ3VLXUSACFHCLDS6QZWN2UU%2F&h=d48f1125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200812/ITWJ3VLXUSACFHCLDS6QZWN2UU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n#FreeAgnes成Twitter榜首 <br />\n日本朝野名人 聲援周庭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/W7mNFXqqz7sN2QmUm2zDjFKZUuk=/1440x961/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GN23UAOHSUO5AUWVM23MD2LIIE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FW7mNFXqqz7sN2QmUm2zDjFKZUuk%3D%2F1440x961%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGN23UAOHSUO5AUWVM23MD2LIIE.gif&h=4d7566cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n周庭被指違反港版國安法的煽惑分裂罪，前晚遭警拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n【瘋狂搜捕】<br />\n<br />\n警方前日除了拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英及集團高層人員，前香港眾志成員周庭（Agnes）亦被指違反港版國安法的煽惑分裂罪被捕。精通日語的周庭在日本知名度高，當地傳媒大篇幅報道她被捕的消息，網民亦發起「#FreeAgnes」標籤行動要求釋放周庭，獲跨界別名人響應，一度成Twitter最熱門榜首。<br />\n<br />\n現年23歲的周庭精通日語，不時接受日本傳媒訪問講述香港社運情況，包括反。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：篩選傳媒被轟 警：會優化<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Flvc3LpR3XuSBsJxNapYsNmN4OY=/1713x689/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2A266INX5F4WOHVJRXYTESK2KE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFlvc3LpR3XuSBsJxNapYsNmN4OY%3D%2F1713x689%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2A266INX5F4WOHVJRXYTESK2KE.gif&h=18f67e36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菅義偉：極憂慮港情況<br />\n<br />\n日本各黨派相繼表態，最大在野黨立憲民主黨黨魁枝野幸男及副黨魁蓮舫都以「#FreeAgnes」推文關注周庭及黎智英被捕，抗議中國打壓香港自由民主侵害人權。枝野幸男稱，不得不說香港問題現已成「對人權及言論自由鎮壓」。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官菅義偉昨日被問到周庭等人被捕時，表示對香港持續的情況。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/tqHIgAibbyXdPjliw580oVQ2FTA=/762x1032/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LNAN26W6KLCF4OUHVZ2I6D4P64.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FtqHIgAibbyXdPjliw580oVQ2FTA%3D%2F762x1032%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLNAN26W6KLCF4OUHVZ2I6D4P64.gif&h=188bdee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本多間大型媒體包括《朝日新聞》均大篇幅報道周庭被捕消息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日議員今召開緊急會議<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：員工遭軟禁監視「我以為我哋係犯」<br />\n<br />\n「日本國會對華政策聯盟」在Twitter宣佈今日將召開緊急會議，商討周庭等人被捕一事，並附上「#FreeAgnes」標籤。<br />\n<br />\n文藝界就有當代藝術家奈良美智，他24小時內四度撐周庭、轉發她被捕的消。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n經典動畫《我係小忌廉》的殿堂級動畫家高田明美，一直也有在Twitter追隨周庭，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n文藝娛樂界聲援<br />\n<br />\n共同社/中央社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/qvvwZ5u62Lj1YKI7TcbB-SrqR-8=/857x1391/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KU5V3KU4VUMTPALFJSF3BLDYAY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FqvvwZ5u62Lj1YKI7TcbB-SrqR-8%3D%2F857x1391%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKU5V3KU4VUMTPALFJSF3BLDYAY.gif&h=ce698c9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n藝術家奈良美智轉發周庭被捕的消息，並呼籲網民關注香港被打壓的問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-JGLc6uylGZ_-eEJexMZB_GEwE0=/693x1499/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2TL7NBH6ZAFO56GFV3Y2EYA2BE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-JGLc6uylGZ_-eEJexMZB_GEwE0%3D%2F693x1499%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2TL7NBH6ZAFO56GFV3Y2EYA2BE.gif&h=96f9c177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曾演出《超人帝拿》的鶴野剛士轉發羅冠聰的Twitter，並留了「#FreeAgnes」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/h3HP0SMQT2sJe104WzVUJIBgPks=/669x1449/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/6IS5L5GEOWCQEDWQXT3YW4HQJE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fh3HP0SMQT2sJe104WzVUJIBgPks%3D%2F669x1449%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F6IS5L5GEOWCQEDWQXT3YW4HQJE.gif&h=a7d4d1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n女星千眼美子轉推貼文要求釋放周庭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Pdpn_JQ6VMfkxjcM1PvI2b0XyeI=/702x1248/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DQNMMJTC22K3ZOZUIZOL5EHPBY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPdpn_JQ6VMfkxjcM1PvI2b0XyeI%3D%2F702x1248%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDQNMMJTC22K3ZOZUIZOL5EHPBY.gif&h=82a3c588&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乙武洋匡在推文說，「無法不去想香港的事，無法入眠」。"},{"pid":"c3001780b172d74f5667d3bd6c391df8c9bf56c1","tid":2152788,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T07:42:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}